With this WIFI weather station, you can get the latest information about the weather. It runs on both battery and solar power and can be operated wirelessly. Its integrated sensor array can deliver temperature and humidity (indoor and outdoor), barometric pressure, rainfall, wind speed and direction as well as UV and light index. The WIFI connectivity allows you to monitor the unit remotely and share the weather data to Weathercloud or Weather Underground. This system is easy to set up which can be hung on the wall or stand on a flat surface. Let this weather station become your personal meteorologist.

column2: • Rainfall data (inch or mm): 1 hour, 24 hours, week, month, and total

This wireless weather station is constructed from high-grade materials, which is built to last whether in your house, garden or backyard. This home weather station can report full weather information, including barometric pressure, wind speed, wind direction, the volume of rain as well as indoor and outdoor temperature and humidity. This system can be operated by battery or solar energy. Mount it on the wall or place it on a flat area. For data accuracy, remember to keep the unit away from any source of heat and obstructions, such as buildings, sidewalks and macadam.
